keyPolicies.policyDescription: A local campaigner who will fight for you.
For a stronger economy - Jackie will fight for action to help our economy, reduce debt and reform taxes and encourage work.
For better public services - Jackie wants the sick get treatment they need and for better schools which give every child a good start in life.
